2 (5) (a) "Net operating revenue" means gross revenue collected by ambulance providers for the
3 delivery of emergency ambulance services, minus amounts deducted for bad debt, charity care, and payer
4 discounts.
5 (b) The term does not include nonpatient service-related revenue.
